        "timestamp": "2019-01-15 17:00:27.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDavesh, Hi, good patch -reviewing now\nreviewing patch - adding more oom committers.\nYou may want to put some evidence for the following\n- that the build is still OK for those components - they come up fine with/without the yaml change - although with is preferrred\n- that the affected pods take the yaml change and now adhere to it.",
