        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-15 17:06:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nessentially anything that helps a committer hit +2 and know the patch was verified help\n\nto help out - run with a change to the policy in \nhttps://git.onap.org/oom/tree/kubernetes/onap/resources/environments/dev.yaml#n40\n\nNegative test:\na way to test this would be to remove one of the images from the docker cache and verify that you get an imagepullerror on the pod expecting the pull if you put \"Never\"  for example",
        "patchset_number": 1
